Package: ctextclassics
Type: Package
Title: Download Pre-Modern Chinese Texts from Ctext.org
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Johnson, Jeremy
Maintainer: Jeremy Johnson <jeremyaaronjohnson@hotmail.com>
Description: Connect to the Ctext.org API and download chapters,
  or complete books of various classic Chinese texts. The intention,
  of this package is to allow for Chinese text analysis utilizing the
  api service and the numerous Chinese works on Ctext.org. Thus,
  'ctextclassics' is not disimilar to the 'gutenbergr' package,
  in that it sources text data for text analysis.
  An internal dataframe 'book_list' allows for the indexing of,
  the lookup calls. Available on github at Jjohn987/ctextclassics
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
Imports: httr (>= 1.2),
  jsonlite (>= 1.1),
  purrr (>= 0.2.4)
Suggests:
  tmcn
URL: https://github.com/Jjohn987/ctextclassics
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr

